	<description>
		<![CDATA[
			<div class="overview-header">
			<h2>
			  <small style="display: block;">Responsive Joomla template for ecommerce  for both Joomla 2.5. and Joomla 3 - <strong>JA Bookshop</strong>.</small>
			</h2>
			<p>A supreme responsive Joomla template for online stores - <strong>JA Bookshop</strong>.</p>
			<p>Coming with flat design and the powerful Mijoshop shopping cart component, this Joomla ecommerce template will 
			definitely spice up your e-stores in the most amazing way.</p>
			<p>Built on the robust T3 Framework with Bootstrap 3 at core, this template is fullly responsive and RTL language 
			layout compatible. <strong>JA Bookshop</strong> features EasyBlog, Megamenu and Off-Canvas navigation along with a number of colors 
			and bonus pages. Also in this template, for the first time we support two new modules: JA MijoShop Product Slider 
			and JA MijoShop Product Accordion.</p>
			</div>
		]]>
	</description>
